WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.230
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.750
doing today? We're going to pray about

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:06.630
some things. But I'm going to tell you,

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:08.950
it's time for the church to wake up. In

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.669
this thing that I've seen taking place,

00:00:11.679 --> 00:00:15.589
I've seen a church—the

00:00:15.589 --> 00:00:15.599
blood-bought,

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:17.870
born-again, blood-bought church of the

00:00:17.870 --> 00:00:17.880
redeemed—standing

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:20.390
up in brush

00:00:20.390 --> 00:00:20.400
arbor

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.029
churches, and a righteousness and a

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:24.470
holiness being preached back in the

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:27.349
pulpits again with people that are

00:00:27.359 --> 00:00:31.189
humbled and weeping at the altar, crying

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:34.470
out for a sovereign God, what

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:37.190
they would call a God of repentance, a

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:41.110
God of recompense to restore

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:44.150
back what the cankerworm ate, to call back,

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:46.150
and we would have a harvest of

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:49.670
souls. Not so much financially motivated,

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:51.630
but

00:00:51.630 --> 00:00:51.640
glory-motivated—a

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:55.430
glorious motivation of just

00:00:55.440 --> 00:00:57.270
saying, 'We're so all out. We're sold out

00:00:57.280 --> 00:01:01.349
for Jesus.'We want a new touch from the

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.910
Father in these brush arbor churches;

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:06.789
we want the glory. We want a

00:01:06.799 --> 00:01:09.590
manifestation of His glory, but it

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.030
will not come with a dirty

00:01:12.040 --> 00:01:14.550
people. You can say what you want to,

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:17.190
but your church is dirty. And the people

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:20.070
don't have a heart

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:20.990
after

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.070
Him. They do not have a heart after the

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:25.990
Father. A lot of them have a

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.510
heart after the world. And the Lord says,

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.910
'Either you are hot or you're cold,

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:34.550
but if you're lukewarm, I will spew you

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:36.310
out of my mouth.'And you say, 'Well,

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:38.670
that's harsh.'No, it's the

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:41.510
word. And it's going to come down to it:

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:43.190
you are going to preach the word, not

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.510
an

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:47.429
opinion. And we either stand by the word

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:50.310
or you get out of the pulpit.

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:52.870
It's time that we rise up like Davids

00:01:52.880 --> 00:01:55.990
and take the land and know that it's

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:59.030
going to take a bulldog personality to

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:01.030
say, 'We're going to stand

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:04.149
for Jesus—all for Jesus, all for Him or

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:06.870
nothing else.'You think,

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:08.469
'Well, we're just going to

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:10.150
limp

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:11.830
by. We're going to get back

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:13.430
in there and we're going to preach them a little bit of

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:13.440
soft, limp, little spoonful of gospel and

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:14.550
just kind of

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.910
nourish people.'No, it's going to

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:24.190
take a bunch of

00:02:24.190 --> 00:02:24.200
meat-eaters.

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:27.110
You say, 'Well, I'm

00:02:27.110 --> 00:02:27.120
vegan.'I

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:28.229
don't care if you're vegan or not.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.390
Whatever. I'm talking about people who

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:32.430
have teeth that eat the meat of the

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:35.589
word. Not a vegan word; I'm talking about

00:02:35.589 --> 00:02:35.599
the

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:37.990
meat of the word. I'm talking about

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:40.470
people getting some common sense here

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.630
and knowing that you've got to

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:44.790
preach righteousness and you've got to

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.030
preach holiness and get it back in the

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:49.110
pulpits and telling people they've got

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:51.509
to rise up and tell that Jesus

00:02:51.519 --> 00:02:53.150
Christ is

00:02:53.160 --> 00:02:56.150
coming, for the harvest is plentiful and

00:02:56.160 --> 00:02:57.869
the laborers are

00:02:57.879 --> 00:03:00.949
few, and the house of cards is coming

00:03:00.959 --> 00:03:07.110
down, folks.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.830
Jesus is

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:11.790
coming. Are you ready for His

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:14.229
return? There's many of you

00:03:14.229 --> 00:03:14.239
who

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:15.990
say that you are, but He has no

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:19.110
idea who you are because you're so far

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:22.509
from Him. You live such a heathen

00:03:22.519 --> 00:03:25.430
lifestyle and you don't even realize

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:27.670
that you are like Lot in Sodom and

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.750
Gomorrah thinking that everything's

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:33.030
okay. And it took Abraham

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:35.350
interceding for Lot in the midst of

00:03:35.350 --> 00:03:35.360
Gomorrah,

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:38.149
crying out to spare

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:41.350
Lot and his family. One man stood in the

00:03:41.350 --> 00:03:41.360
gap,

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:44.149
like I told you. One person stood

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:47.350
in the gap for the person as Lot and his

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.270
family. And if he wouldn't have been

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:51.589
standing in the gap, Lot would

00:03:51.599 --> 00:03:53.830
have been burned up just like

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.910
everybody else was.

00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:58.869
He didn't even know judgment was coming

00:03:58.879 --> 00:04:01.509
because he'd become so familiar with

00:04:01.519 --> 00:04:05.190
Sodom and Gomorrah. He did not know that

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:07.750
all the things were coming because he

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:10.350
was so in

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:13.030
compromise. He

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:16.390
fixed his

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:18.189
tent towards

00:04:18.199 --> 00:04:20.870
Sodom and he thought, 'Man, this is a

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:22.710
nice city. I love living in this. This

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:25.670
is nice.'And every day he woke up

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:28.550
seeing all around him. And as he did, he

00:04:28.550 --> 00:04:28.560
became

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:31.830
colder and

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:34.070
colder. And it took a man standing on

00:04:34.080 --> 00:04:37.189
the hill saying, 'Would you spare

00:04:37.189 --> 00:04:37.199
them?'And

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:39.510
God had mercy and removed

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:41.830
his family. But his wife was so

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.590
familiar she looked back and she turned

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:46.070
to a pillar of salt. Will you be one

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:48.150
that turns to a pillar of salt as

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.150
you're crying out for that which was so

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:53.749
important around you?

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:56.150
Everything is so important to you. I

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:57.990
hear the Spirit of the Lord say, 'But am

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.790
I important to

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:03.230
you? Am I important to you?'says the

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:07.110
Lord as your house of cards begins

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:10.550
to crumble, just like Lot's wife turned

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:12.790
and looked to Sodom and

00:05:12.790 --> 00:05:12.800
it

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:14.870
was so important to her because she had

00:05:14.870 --> 00:05:14.880
become

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:17.590
so accustomed to it.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:19.430
You've become accustomed to Sodom and

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:21.749
Gomorrah, ladies and gentlemen. And the

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:24.469
Lord tells me, 'Great judgment's

00:05:24.479 --> 00:05:26.469
coming in these areas.'And you say,

00:05:26.479 --> 00:05:27.990
'Well, I'll stand in the gap like

00:05:27.990 --> 00:05:28.000
Abraham.'But

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:30.350
God's calling you out from

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.950
Sodom. God's calling you out from

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:35.110
Gomorrah. He's calling you out and He's

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.029
telling you it's time to come up higher

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:38.710
or you're going to stay back here and

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:41.510
turn to that pillar of

00:05:41.510 --> 00:05:41.520
salt.

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:43.590
Are you going to turn your

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:46.070
back on Sodom and Gomorrah just like Lot

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:48.629
had to and run to the mountains with the

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.629
angels, or are you going to keep looking

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:53.110
back because it was familiar to you and

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:56.070
you got accustomed to it? I'm telling

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:59.029
you, it's time to come out of that. It's

00:05:59.039 --> 00:06:01.029
time to come up in the glory and sit at

00:06:01.039 --> 00:06:03.150
His altar and weep before Him and say,

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:06.749
'Jesus, all of You and none of

00:06:06.759 --> 00:06:10.870
me. All of You and none of me. I don't

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:13.110
want any of this world. I don't want to

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:15.029
be so spiritually minded that I'm no

00:06:15.039 --> 00:06:18.550
earthly good.'Some people say, 'I don't

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.550
see that you could be too spiritually

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:21.629
minded,

00:06:21.629 --> 00:06:21.639
folks.'You

00:06:21.639 --> 00:06:23.909
say, 'I don't want to be too

00:06:23.919 --> 00:06:25.350
spiritually minded. I don't want to be

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:27.510
too spiritual because I

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:30.590
won't be able to relate with

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:34.070
Sodom. I want to relate with Sodom. I

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:36.150
want to relate with Gomorrah because I

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:37.830
want to be able to

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:39.909
minister to them because if I

00:06:39.919 --> 00:06:42.070
get too spiritual and I get too holy

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:42.080
roller

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:44.150
on you, we won't be able to

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:45.350
minister because they won't be able to

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.309
relate with

00:06:47.309 --> 00:06:47.319
us.'You're

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:50.990
wrong. You're

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:53.909
wrong. He's calling us to be the salt of

00:06:53.919 --> 00:06:55.909
the earth. He's calling us to have a

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:58.629
backbone like a crowbar. And

00:06:58.639 --> 00:07:00.790
He's calling us to preach the good news

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.110
to the world. And I'm telling you, when

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.110
all hell breaks out, ladies and

00:07:05.120 --> 00:07:07.510
gentlemen, when all crap hits

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:09.670
the fan, they're going to be coming for

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:12.390
the people who have the light, like

00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:12.400
Moses'face

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:14.870
was shining with the glory

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:16.950
of God. They're going to come to you

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:18.550
because they're going to say, 'I

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.469
remember when I used to think you were a

00:07:20.479 --> 00:07:22.629
holy roller and you were too religious,

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:25.589
because right now I need a God that's

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:28.150
real,

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:30.309
right now because of all the hell that's

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:32.629
going on around me and the economy's

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:34.550
crashing and the people are

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:37.029
getting sick and dying. I need a God

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:37.870
that's

00:07:37.880 --> 00:07:41.909
real. Not a God that is a lukewarm God.

00:07:41.919 --> 00:07:44.469
Not a God that I have my

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:46.629
tent fixed to Sodom because I want to be

00:07:46.639 --> 00:07:49.550
just a little bit like them so I'm

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:53.790
relatable. I want to be like

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:56.790
Jesus. And there was no compromise in

00:07:56.800 --> 00:08:01.510
Him at all. He was the rock and upon Him

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:03.670
He said, 'You will build my

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:05.830
church and the gates of hell will not

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:09.469
prevail against it.'Not a sinking sand

00:08:09.479 --> 00:08:13.110
gospel, but a gospel that is

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:15.909
built on the word, the foundation of the

00:08:15.919 --> 00:08:19.110
word that Jesus Christ is coming and

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:21.589
that Jesus is our Savior. He's our

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:24.390
Healer. He's our Deliverer. And He is

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:27.070
not a compromising God. That is just a

00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:29.830
lukewarm, spoonful gospel. We're

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:31.510
going to just barely feed you, and

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:33.509
you're going to get your little baby

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:35.750
pampers... No, no, no.

00:08:35.760 --> 00:08:37.990
It's time to feed the meat of the word

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:40.550
to the people so that they're able to

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.630
stand and stand when all there else to

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:45.110
do is stand. Therefore, it's time to

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:49.550
stand and have a backbone in this

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:52.310
generation. Woe to you that don't.

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:54.710
You're going to go home early. I'm telling

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:57.110
you. Woe to you who don't because you'll

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.670
go home early. You won't be able to

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:02.030
stand because the devourer is coming for

00:09:02.040 --> 00:09:06.150
you. The great devourer will come for you.

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:08.470
Satan comes as a roaring lion seeking

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:10.870
whom he may devour. Is your house full

00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:13.430
of compromise that he can devour you?

00:09:13.440 --> 00:09:15.269
Because as for me and my house, we will

00:09:15.279 --> 00:09:17.829
serve the Lord. And we have a bloodline

00:09:17.839 --> 00:09:19.990
out there that says, 'Satan, thus far

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.389
and no further.'You will not tread on

00:09:22.399 --> 00:09:24.350
us. We tread on

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:27.190
you. We have authority over you in this

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:29.430
house. Do you have that authority in

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.430
your house? Are you still in Sodom and

00:09:31.430 --> 00:09:31.440
Gomorrah

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:33.910
and you think you're okay?

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:35.590
Because I'm telling you, ladies and

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:37.350
gentlemen, there's a lot of you that

00:09:37.350 --> 00:09:37.360
are

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:39.670
in there. I hear this by the Spirit of

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:42.070
God. You better be listening for

00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:43.990
what I have seen coming. If you are in

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.150
Sodom and there's somebody out

00:09:46.150 --> 00:09:46.160
there—your

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:47.990
grandma is out there praying for

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.949
you, 'Oh, have mercy on Johnny out

00:09:50.949 --> 00:09:50.959
there'—you

00:09:50.959 --> 00:09:53.110
better thank God for her. 'Oh,

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:56.550
have mercy on little Susie'or whoever

00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:58.150
because they're up there: 'Lord, please

00:09:58.160 --> 00:09:59.150
have

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:02.710
mercy. Please have mercy.'And you're in

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:05.430
there just partying in Sodom, 'I'm over

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:08.350
here just enjoying myself.'You're a

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:11.550
fool. God have mercy on

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:14.230
you. The angels of the

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:16.790
Lord are sent to protect

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:18.710
them.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.550
I don't know who this is for today, but

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:22.430
I pray it stirs

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:25.030
you. I don't want to be too spiritually

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:28.069
minded that I'm no earthly good. God

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:30.910
have mercy on you.

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:36.069
I'm all in. Are you all in? Are you

00:10:36.079 --> 00:10:39.790
all in for Jesus? All to Jesus, I

00:10:39.800 --> 00:10:45.630
surrender. All to Him, I freely

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:49.269
give. I've seen a great storm coming and

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:52.150
it's still on the horizon. It may be

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:56.069
delayed by some months, whether or not

00:10:56.079 --> 00:10:58.870
it's a year or whatever. When you're

00:10:58.880 --> 00:11:00.790
looking into the spirit realm, ladies

00:11:00.800 --> 00:11:02.550
and gentlemen, there's a depth

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:04.550
perception about things that I'm still

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:07.110
learning. But I can assure you, I see a

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:10.069
storm on the horizon. And I'm telling

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:13.110
you, it's a time like never before to

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:15.990
fall at the altars, falling at

00:11:15.990 --> 00:11:16.000
Jesus'feet

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:18.910
and saying, 'All to Jesus, I

00:11:18.920 --> 00:11:22.790
surrender. All to Thee, I humbly give. I

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:25.269
give You my heart. I give You my

00:11:25.269 --> 00:11:25.279
soul.'Today,

00:11:25.279 --> 00:11:27.509
Lord, I serve You with everything

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:30.710
I have inside of me. I am not worried

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:32.790
and I'm not moved by what I see around

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:34.550
me. I'm moved by what the Word of God

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:36.470
says. Because when the winds and the

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:40.949
storms blow, my anchor is

00:11:40.959 --> 00:11:44.310
in the Lord Jesus Christ. My

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:48.790
